Title: Highway
DateModified: '2019-03-01'
DatePublished: '2019-03-01'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/highway
SetInCountry: India
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Abhijit Boricha
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "Where we are going, i dont want to go there. where i came from, i dont want\
  \ to go back either. But this highway, i love it so much.i hope it never ends.the\
  \ place i used to live, doing 9 to 5 job was a cage. But on this highway i feel\
  \ free here.when i am on my deathbed, i dont want to be that guy who says,\u201D\
  i wish i couldve do that when i had time\u201D. Ill die with memories. Memories\
  \ never dies."
